DSym_TuneControl  (&4588D)
#Parent DSym_
=>	R0 =	-1 to read status
	 	other, to set (lower byte)

<=	R0 = previous tune status (0= off, \<>0= on)

This call controls the tune decoder. Off means the tune decoder won't let play notes anymore, you can still play custom notes. Current notes still playing.